{
  "stem": "1502.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 140,
      "text": "They would kick them in the back to get them used to brutal-- to being dealt brutally.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 141,
      "text": "The first procedure was the-- on the left side of the camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 142,
      "text": "There was the place they called the Reception of [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 143,
      "text": "That was the reception for new prisoners.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 144,
      "text": "The reception was manned by prisoners, by Jewish girls that they had caught.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 145,
      "text": "And they decided to give them a job in the-- in the reception.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 146,
      "text": "So these girls were saved until they would decide to deport them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 147,
      "text": "Some of them were there a year or more or two years.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 148,
      "text": "And so, you had to-- like, these girls were registering us, name, the-- the-- where we were caught and so forth.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 149,
      "text": "I don't remember exactly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 150,
      "text": "But it was some kind of registration.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 151,
      "text": "You also had to give them your identity card, your rationing card, your money, your gold if you had.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 152,
      "text": "I had a gold watch.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 153,
      "text": "I gave them the gold watch.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 154,
      "text": "People had diamonds or jewelry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 155,
      "text": "Everything was taken away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 156,
      "text": "It was put in an envelope with the name of the person.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 157,
      "text": "And at that reception, it was quite brutal.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 158,
      "text": "They were beating up people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 159,
      "text": "They were kicking.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 160,
      "text": "They-- they-- it was-- it was a-- a-- a torture to get through the reception.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 161,
      "text": "Once you were through the reception, they let you into your place, where you-- into your quarters.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 162,
      "text": "The quarters were-- they-- they-- what they called [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 163,
      "text": "[GERMAN] means a-- a room, a ball room-- I would say, a hall.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 164,
      "text": "And the hall had numbers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 165,
      "text": "This was from-- from one-- I don't remember to how much.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 166,
      "text": "But I remember there was this one and there was a 13.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 167,
      "text": "So there must have been, maybe, 20-- 20 halls.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 168,
      "text": "Each hall could take up to 100 people.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
